# pcr-s1 (2026-07-11-pipeline-conflict-reduction, AC5):
# decisions.md is a shared append-only log. Two branches that each
# independently append a new decision entry to the same file collided on
# git's default line-based merge even though the entries themselves don't
# overlap and order between them doesn't matter. `merge=union` tells git to
# keep both sides' added lines instead of raising a conflict for this file.
artefacts/**/decisions.md merge=union
